_name}</b> has been created successfully. Here are the details:</div><div class=server-info><h3>Server Details</h3><p><b>Server Name:</b> {server_name}<br><b>IP Address:</b> {server_ip}<br><b>Panel URL:</b> {panel_url}</p><p>To manage your server, log in to your dashboard.</p><a href={dashboard_url} class=cta-button>Go to Dashboard</a></div><div class=footer><p>This email was sent to {email}<p>Â© 2024-2025 {app_name}. All rights reserved.<p><a href={support_url}>Support</a></div></div>'
